{
  "stem": "1085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In that book published about me, there is a map.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the map shows [INAUDIBLE], exactly where it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- I must have been caught probably the end of September, until probably the late October.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, the non-commissioned officers stayed in the church, you know, former [INAUDIBLE], of course, reconstructed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the officers were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed in some huts, primitive, or tents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the commandeer announced publicly that non-- all non-commissioned officers who are of German descent or who were born on the territories incorporated into the Third Reich, if they so desire, please come to his office tomorrow if you want to be-- go to the German side.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, the German general staff committed itself-- also public.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was public that all war prisoners of Ukrainian descent, Belarussian, or Russian, who wanted to go to the Soviet side of Poland, they would be allowed, men for men.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The same [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, so I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because at that time, I was born in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time, Lodz was already incorporated into the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not the-- as general government incorporated and even renamed as Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE]-- so I had a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I realized it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a good point by me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would realize from the very beginning to get out of the Soviet hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, we're not so much trusted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I considered Germany a civilized country, you know, and a higher level than Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I prefer to go to the German side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, to make it short, we were cutting the woods to make a living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to work in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I exchanged my officer's boots which betrayed me as an officer with some soldier non-commissioned officer my size, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
